description: Sgt. Major takes Donna miles away from the villa and into the Mexican hills to break her resistant spirit, and has a grueling day in the hot dry heat of Mexico. Donna gets her money's worth for the fantasy that she paid for, and is determined to beat Sgt Major at his game. Proud and defiant, she holds out longer then any before her. However, even she cannot stand the Sgt's onslaught forever and finally she is broken. The Sgt uses and abuses poor Donna after she surrenders her will. Fucked, flogged, made to come and even made to ask permission to cum is what Donna is reduced too. She will return to the villa a much more pliable subject.
title: Cabo, the Return. Part 8
